1.PROMPT for WeightOne, PriceOne and WeightTwo, PriceTwo
2. GET WeightOne, PriceOne, WeightTwo, PriceTwo
3. IF  PriceOne < PriceTwo AND WeightOne >= WeightTwo THEN

            
              RESULT =  Package 1 is at better price 

            ELSE 
IF PriceOne > PriceTwo AND WeightOne <= WeightTwo THEN

            
               RESULT =  Package 2 is at better price 
            
          		  ELSE

                          		 RESULT = Both packets are the same price 
            
END IF
     END IF

           


DISPLAY RESULT
